{"serial": "41021", "department_serial": 38, "code": "BA5040", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Enterprise Resource Planning", "ch": "企業資源規劃"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Hsu, Ping-Yu", "Tsai, Wen-Hsien", "Chou, Huey-Wen", "Sheen, Gwo-Ji", "Hsu, Wen-Chin"], "ch": ["許秉瑜", "蔡文賢", "周惠文", "沈國基", "許文錦"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 5, "session": ["2", "3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "I", "room": "204"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 120, "department": {"ch": "企業管理學系", "en": "Department of Business Administration"}, "system": {"ch": "碩博同修", "en": "Master/Doctoral Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 8, "selected": 73, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程旨在向管理學院的學生介紹ERP知識。 由於ERP是電子商務的核心系統，涵蓋了商業實踐的各個方面，介紹ERP系統的基本觀念與各組成模組的運作概念，作為修習ERP進一步課程的基礎。\n\n因此課程涵蓋了電子商務應用的所有基本商業理論，如銷售、生產計劃、會計、人力資源管理和電子商務體系結構。\n參加課程的學生應具備會計和生產計劃的基本知識。 課程將介紹這些知識在電子商務中的應用，但不再介紹管理知識。 該課程屬於中國ERP學會教育計畫的一部分，參加課程的學生可以在暑假參加認證考試。\n成績將根據期中、期末考以及班級出現率來決定。\n課程包括以下主題：\n ERP簡介\n 業務流程建模介紹\n ERP中的財務模組\n ERP物流模組\n ERP 人力資源模組\n ERP實施\n ERP 與電子商務及數位轉型", "en": "The course is intended to introduce ERP knowledge to students in management schools. As ERP is the core e-business system and encompass all aspects of business practice, the course covers the e-business applications of all basic business theory, such as sales, production planning, accounting, human resource management and e-business architecture. \nStudents taking the courses are supposed to have basic knowledge of accounting and production planning. The course will introduce the application of the knowledge in e-business but will not introduce the management knowledge again. The course is part of the education program of Chinese ERP society and students taking the course can take the certification exam in the summer break.\nThe grade will be given based on the midterm and final examines and the show up ratio in the classes.\nThe course include following topics:\nERP introduction\nBusiness process modeling introduction\nERP in financial modules\nERP in logistic modules\nERP in HR modules\nERP implementation\nERP and e-Business ＆ Digital Transformation"}, "outline": {"ch": "2/23課程介紹\n銷售與配銷模組\n3/01企業資源規劃簡介\n3/08企業流程管理與ERP\n3/15生產規劃與控制\n3/22企業之採購管理\n3/29庫存管理系統\n4/05春假\n4/12期中考週\n4/19ERP財務會計模組\n4/26成本控制模組\n5/03人力資源模組\n5/10企業雲端運算與應用\n5/17ERP系統導入的兩個案例\n5/24系統導入\n5/31從ERP到企業數位轉型\n6/08期末考週", "en": "2/23 Course Introduction\nSales and Distribution Module\n3/01 Introduction to Enterprise Resource Planning\n3/08 Enterprise process management and ERP\n3/15 Production planning and control\n3/22 Enterprise Procurement Management\n3/29 Inventory Management System\n4/05 Spring Break\n4/12 midterm exam week\n4/19 ERP financial accounting module\n4/26 Cost Control Module\n5/03 Human Resources Module\n5/10 Enterprise cloud computing and applications\n5/17 Two cases of ERP system introduction\n5/24 System import\n5/31 From ERP to enterprise digital transformation\n6/08 Final exam week"}, "textbook": {"ch": "ERP企業資源規劃導論 第六版 \n(2022/07/27出版)\nISBN：9786263242272國立中央大學\n管理學院ERP中心碁峰出版\n教科書網址：https://www.gotop.com.tw/books/BookDetails.aspx?Types=v＆bn=AEE040500", "en": "1.“Textbook： Enterprise Resource Planning V.6 ( 2022/07/27 Gotop )\n\n2.Reference: Enterprise Resource Planning for Manufactoring :https://www.gotop.com.tw/books/BookDetails.aspx?Types=v＆bn=AEE040500"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "10", "en": "10"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授", "en": ["Lecture"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "期中考試 30％\n期末考試 30％\n上課出席 40％", "en": "Midterm exam 30％\nFinal exam 30％\nClass attendance 40％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "研究室I1-736 分機6168", "en": "Research Room I1-736 extension 6168"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "為了鼓勵同學報考ERP證照考試，有報名考ERP規劃師證照同學，期末考分數加20分", "en": "In order to encourage students to apply for the ERP certification exam, students who apply for the ERP plan